        }
      ],
      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A paediatric resident is reviewing metabolic disorders for an upcoming exam and is focusing on enzyme deficiencies associated with various paediatric diseases. Match the following paediatric diseases with their corresponding enzyme deficiencies:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cerebellum-web-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/public/images/2024/04/02/picture13.jpg\" style=\"height:165px; width:700px\" /></p>",
